para_trans: Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk
Reference: GOVERNMENT ORDER NO. REPRECTION-2022 / Q. 72 / Q. 14, D. 16.02.2023.

Shri Sanjay Dattatray Kamlakar, Joint Secretary has been appointed as Member Secretary, Maharashtra State Commission for Scheduled Castes and Scheduled Tribes, Mumbai, under the Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance on deputation for a period of 2 years with effect from the date he assumes charge of his office. The period of deputation of Mr. Kamalakar to the said post is d. Expires on 20.02.2025.

2. Now, by this order, Mr. Sanjay Dattatray Kamlakar, Joint Secretary, has been posted as Member Secretary, Maharashtra State Commission for Scheduled Castes and Tribes, Mumbai. From 21.02.2025 onwards, Mr. Kamalakar's appointment was followed by his retirement i.e. 30.11.2025 is being extended beyond this period.
This Government Order is published on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
